<HEADLINE>
FT  19 JAN 94 / UK Company News: Aberforth Smaller
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Basic net asset value per share of the Aberforth Smaller Companies Trust
stood at 188.6p at the December 31, against 165.1p at the interim stage and
122.8p at end-1992.
Total revenue for the year fell to Pounds 4.72m (Pounds 5.57m). Available
revenue amounted to Pounds 2.46m (Pounds 3.27m), giving earnings per share
of 4.36p (5.8p).
A same-again final dividend of 2.5p is proposed to maintain the total at
4.6p.
</TEXT>
