FT  19 JAN 94 / UK Company News: YRM deficit rises to Pounds 1.2m
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
In his first statement since taking over as chairman of YRM, the building
design consultancy, Mr Tony Hunt unveiled an increase in losses from Pounds
498,000 to Pounds 1.19m pre-tax for the half year to end-October.
