   Year                             Richter scale
 -------------------------------------------------
1  1906   San Francisco                  8.3
2  1952   Tehachapi-Bakersfield          7.7
3  1927   Offshore San Luis Obispo       7.7
4  1992   Landers                        7.4
5  1923   North Coast                    7.2
6  1989   San Francisco                  7.1
7  1980   Eureka                         7.0
8  1950   Imperial Valley                6.7
9  1994   Los Angeles                    6.6
10 1971   San Fernando                   6.6
11 1992   Los Angeles                    6.3
12 1987   Los Angeles                    5.9
 -------------------------------------------------
               THE RICHTER SCALE
 -------------------------------------------------
8    Capable of tremendous damage
7    Widespread damage
     Monday's quake: 6.6
6    Severe damage
5    Considerable damage
4    Moderate damage
3.5  Some local damage
 -------------------------------------------------
Source: Associated Press and Reuters
