and Gilardini's BPD Defensa e Spazio of Italy to supply advanced air bag
inflators to European manufacturers.
The venture will be based in Colleferro, Italy, and initially will supply
Fiat in Italy and Opel in Germany.
Each company owns one third of the venture. It is scheduled to begin pilot
production in late 1994 and will be able to produce more than 2m inflators
annually.
