</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Shares in Soundtracs rose 7p to 80p yesterday after the USM-traded
professional electronic audio equipment and loudspeaker group announced a 76
per cent jump in annual pre-tax profits as it benefited from the
introduction of new products.
Mr Todd Wells, chairman, said the increase - from Pounds 350,385 to Pounds
