Turnover for the 12 months to November 6 improved 34 per cent to Pounds
5.51m (Pounds 4.11m).
Earnings per share emerged at 4.09p (2.45p) and a proposed fiinal dividend
of 1.48p brings the total for the year to 2.4p (2.2p).
